description: Through divine providence, Rhode Island has inherited Anchorage, Alaska’s Nina Reed, renowned Pastry Chef and Food Network’s Sweet Genius Guest Star. Using her inherent genius, she’s providing the people of Providence with her sweet selection of speciality desserts; cookies, pies, tarts, cakes/cupcakes, and more! She can transform any beer, cocktail, wine, or beverage into one of her pleasing pastries, and thus has a whopping 40 flavors of cupcakes to offer, including Rum & Coke, Strawberry Cheesecake, Kahlua, Spicy Chocolate, Salty Bacon, Car Bomb, and so, so much more. Get ready to exclaim that these treats are fantastic and there won’t be anything sarcastic about it!
name: Sarcastic Sweets
